IMPORTANT: Individual Solutions and Their Licenses

This framework integrates several open-source talking-head solutions. Each solution
maintains its own license. Please review and comply with each solution's license
before use:

1. SadTalker
   Repository: https://github.com/OpenTalker/SadTalker
   License: Check repository for current license terms

2. Wav2Lip
   Repository: https://github.com/Rudrabha/Wav2Lip
   License: Research and Personal Use Only (Non-Commercial)
   Note: Commercial use requires separate permission from authors

3. EchoMimic
   Repository: https://github.com/antgroup/echomimic
   License: Check repository for current license terms

4. V-Express
   Repository: https://github.com/tencent-ailab/V-Express
   License: Check repository for current license terms

5. Audio2Head
   Repository: https://github.com/wangsuzhen/Audio2Head
   License: Check repository for current license terms

6. Coqui TTS
   Repository: https://github.com/coqui-ai/TTS
   License: MPL 2.0 (Mozilla Public License 2.0)

7. Piper TTS
   Repository: https://github.com/rhasspy/piper
   License: MIT License

Please ensure you comply with all applicable licenses before using this framework
for commercial purposes or distributing derivative works.
